  "texts": [
    "Interviewees talked about other tools as much as about ChatGPT and for these interviewees, it was early days with ChatGPT.",
    "Many had used it to only a limited extent.",
    "Nevertheless, there was evidence of ChatGPT being employed throughout the writing process.",
    "There were frequent mentions of uses to: • rephrase text and check grammar Central uses that ChatGPT was uniquely good at was gaining an understanding of an assignment brief and then structuring ideas: This is the topic and I first use ChatGPT to give me some idea about this topic.",
    "And actually, when I saw this topic, I didn't really understand it."
  ]
}